WRITING.TITLE: Mad Men Series Finale
WRITING.TEXT: I just finished the last episode of Mad Men and I don't know what to think. The whole time watching the series I kept trying to figure Don out. I think he was a lost person who never really figured out his way until the end. I kept thinking the whole time how confused, lost, and empty he was and how he just used money, sex, and liquor to fill those hole's in his life. In the last episode he was talking to Stephanie before she took off on him and he said "I understand people." but he never seemed to really understand himself. Or maybe he did and he just chose to deal with it in a way the he saw fit. This episode left me hanging, I feel like I need one more to sort everything out. I guess maybe he finally found his happiness, but I don't know. I'm just sitting here in a daze thinking about it.
